  "title": "Assembly Technician (Urgent!/East/Up $3.3k!)",
  "description": "<p><strong>The Opportunity</strong></p><ul><li>Opportunity to be part of a global semiconductor MNC</li><li>Shift: Monday to Friday, 7:00am – 4:30pm or 4pm-1:30am (Extra shift allowance up to $550 per month)</li><li>Location: East, Changi/Tampines</li><li>Transporation provided</li><li>12 months (contract extension subject to performance)</li><li>Salary up to $3.3k+!</li></ul><p><strong>Job Scope</strong></p><ul><li>Work in a cleanroom environment and handle testing/assembly equipment</li><li>Perform maintenance, troubleshooting, and routine upkeep of tools and machines</li><li>Set up, calibrate, and prepare equipment for operations</li><li>Read and interpret electro‑mechanical diagrams, drawings, and basic schematics</li><li>Conduct precise measurements within tight tolerances and support other assigned tasks</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>NITEC, Higher NITEC, or Diploma in any related engineering fields</li><li>Relevant experience in assembly, build, testing, and preventive maintenance is an advantage</li><li>Candidates with or without prior experience are welcome to apply</li></ul><p><strong>Next Step</strong></p><p>Prepare your updated resume, send to the following email: eugene.chia@adecco.com or contact +65 87230071 for quick response</p><p>*Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted*<br /></p><p>Eugene Chia</p><p>Direct Line: 6697 7809</p><p>EA License No: 91C2918</p><p>Personnel Registration Number: R24124644</p>",
